		...
	</p>
        <p n="7-9">
		Eight year of the victorious king Aparājitavarmappōttairayar.
	</p>
        <p n="9-13">
		The gold that ... has given for the Mahādeva of Tiruvoṟṟiyūr: sixthy <foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign>s of a purity <supplied reason="subaudible">tested</supplied> on the village <supplied reason="subaudible">touch</supplied>stone.
	</p>
        <p n="13-29">
